# Frontend — Next.js

## Stack

- Next.js App Router, TypeScript strict, Tailwind CSS, shadcn/ui
- Charts: Recharts (not Plotly)
- API calls go through `frontend/lib/api.ts`

## Design tokens

- Primary green: `#2E7D32` (see `designsystem.md`)
- Risk colors: low=green, medium=yellow, high=orange, critical=red

## UX

- Screen IDs and layouts: `ekran-haritasi.md` (38 screens; MVP-20 first).
- Shell / SourceBadge / ConfirmGate: `designsystem.md` §28A.
- Dashboard must answer three questions at a glance: status / what to do / why.
- UI copy in Turkish; explain technical terms with tooltips.
- Label simulation and test data sources clearly on every relevant screen.
- Critical actions (start irrigation, lab confirm) require a confirmation modal.
- Mobile = responsive of the same route; do not create parallel mobile-only pages.

## Components

- Prefer functional components and existing shadcn/ui primitives.
- Keep forms validated with clear Turkish error messages.
